betterquesting:10.desc:8: The Wireless Charging Antenna is an upgrade from the Wireless Charger in the way that it has a bigger range.
你在这个包中需要的主要东西之一是怪物掉落。 要获得它们，您需要建造一个封闭的房间，在那里可以生成怪物。
您还不能制作普通的熔炉，因此对于烹饪和冶炼，您将需要下一个最好的东西：泥炉。 它的工作原理与普通熔炉一样，但使用的燃料是普通熔炉的 3 倍。

为了从Sky Resources和其他一些模组制作许多基本物品，您将§r
需要建造一个多方块氧化结构。

您可以在Sky Resources 2指南中了解如何执行此操作以及如何
使用它。

您可以按住右键单击并松开抽水器，从树叶、雪或仙人掌中收集水。

  你可以通过shift+右击来放置水，并用它制作一个无限的水源。
现在你有了水和熔岩，你可以制作一个传统的刷石机。
使用碎石杵，您可以将某些材料杵成其他材料。

要从Sky Resources的炼金术部分开始，您将需要制作炼金灌注台。 有了它，您将能够制作许多不同的炼金术物品。

但是，要使其发挥作用，您将需要一种催化剂，例如低级炼金粉尘。 每个配方都会消耗一定量的催化剂，用绿色条表示。 每个催化剂都有一个产量，它决定了每个配方中紫色条的填充量，当满时会给你一个输出。
石制为您的氧化提供更高的最大热量单位，而石头氧化加热器降低了每个热量单位使用的燃料量，以及每个配方使用的热量单位，但这将不能再使用活板门。
岩浆石接触水晶液时会掉落圆石。
通过将水注入泥土中，您可以制作粘土或压缩粘土（通过将其注入压缩泥土中）。
既然你有一个冷凝器结构，用水晶液和铁炼金矿粉，你就可以制作铁锭了。
The Enhanced Wireless Charging Antenna has a better range than the regular one and can even have its range expanded in a certain direction with Extensions.
虽然您可以在树苗周围扭动或冲刺以加快生长速度，但您可以对它们使用自然物质使它们立即生长。
End Steel is an end-game EIO alloy made with Obsidian, End Stone and Dark Steel. Darl Steel is another alloy ,made with Iron, Coal and Obsidian.
要制造红石，您将需要 880 HU，而铁制框架可以让您达到。
这可以从一些mod中解锁一些物品，这些mod将帮助您进行早期游戏自动化。
为了让被动生物生成并获得不同的种子，你需要制作一个草方块。
现在您可以制作烈焰粉，您可以将其制作成方块并将其放在火把上方以获得熔岩。 熔化它可能需要几分钟，但如果幸运的话，它甚至可能只需要几秒钟。

This is everything you need in order to construct the smallest possible Extreme Reactor.

 Extreme Reactors use Yellorium for generating large amounts of power.
你可以用碎石杵将沙砾变成沙子。
你可以用碎石杵将圆石变成沙砾。

为了制造锭，您将需要搭建冷凝器结构。
您可以在Sky Resources的指南中了解如何进行最基本的设置。 请记住，底部方块可以是任何容器，例如箱子。
通过破坏草，您可以获得许多不同有用作物的种子。

通过生命灌注，您可以使用生命值和 2 个特定物品来
制造进一步所需的植物。

  如果你从岩浆岛开始，你已经有了砂岩灌注石，但如果你没有，你将需要通过氧化制作脱水仙人掌，然后用抽水器将其水化。

您可以在 Sky Resources 指南中了解有关其工作原理的更多信息。
这个任务将解锁 Aether Legacy 和 Open Blocks。
您可以使用带有铁制框架的氧化器制作的另一个东西是地狱岩。
The Enhanced Chassis allows you to enhance your industrial EIO machines.
蚯蚓可以通过耕地获得。 他们可以不断在3x3区域内创建农田。
现在你有了地狱岩外壳，你可以用火药和烈焰粉制作荧石。
木锥会伤害生物，直到它们达到半颗心。
石锥会伤害怪物并杀死它们。

使用冰箱，您可以冷冻不同的材料以将它们变成其他材料。 这也是制作泥土的最简单方法之一。

  如果你从雪岛开始，你已经有了这个，但如果你没有，你可以通过氧化来制造雪，shift+右键点击雪块来复制它们并制作一个迷你冰箱。

虽然迷你冰箱可以工作，但并不是那么快。 最好制作一个多方块铁制冰箱
来更快地冷冻更多的东西。
金锥会伤害生物并使它们掉落经验。
钻石锥会伤害生物并使它们掉落玩家专用的掉落物，例如战利品。
坩埚投料器最多可容纳一组水晶碎片，并在坩埚有空间时自动将它们扔进坩埚，这样您就不必再每隔几分钟就去那里扔 3 个碎片。
The Basic Solar Panel can generate 4RF/t during the day.
The Hybrid Solar Panel can generate 64RF/t during the day.
The Tinker's Hammer for connecting certain Embers blocks.
坩埚用于将烈焰粉块熔化为熔岩，将水晶碎片熔化为水晶液。
使用生命灌注，您可以制作可以长出史莱姆的树苗。
紫色史莱姆比蓝色史莱姆更有用，所以你也应该为它制作一个树苗。
要制作拥有火焰保护的匠魂工具，您将需要岩浆史莱姆。 幸运的是，您也可以为它制作树苗。
要达到大量的热量单位，您将需要一个地狱岩外壳。 请记住，它的效率非常低。
发射器很好，但连续按下按钮让它掉落物品并不好玩。 不过不用担心。 您现在可以制作不需要红石信号的快速漏斗（除非您想将其关闭）。 请记住，它不能与木制或石头氧化加热器一起使用。
The Sturdy Casing is needed for making most Forestry machines.
The Carpenter uses power, items and a certain fluid to make a certain item.
The Squeezer uses power from Squeezing certain items.
The Pipette is a great tool for moving around fluids early on. The great thing about it is that there's not a minimum amount of fluid it can hold.
储存液体的最简单方法是在桶中。
氧化产物收集器自动收集氧化配方输出的物品，这样您就不必在每个配方后将其清空。 请记住，它不能与木制或石头氧化加热器一起使用。
The Advanced Solar Panel, besides for generating a good bit of RF during the day, can also generate a bit during the night.
Now that you have a Carpenter and a Squeezer, you can make Impregnated Casings, needed for some Forestry and Binnie's Mods machines, and Impregnated Sticks, needed for Impregnated Frames.
To be able to construct all the Multiblock IE machines, you are going to need an Engineer's Hammer.
For making Coke Coal and Creosote Oil, you are going to need a Coke Oven.
For making Steel and starting off with mid-game, you are going to need a multiblock Blast Furnace.
The Projector allows you to see where everything in an IE multiblock goes in the world, helping you build it.

Demon Ingots are obtained by throwing Gold into Lava that's surrounded by Nether Bricks on all sides, besides the top and bottom. Keep in mind that it has a small chance to eat up your Gold without giving you anything.
Light Matter machines are the most efficient Sky Resources machines.
The Ultimate Solar Panel can generate over 1kRF/t during the day.
The Plasma Generator uses Plasma to generate a lot of RF.
The Quantum Solar Panel is the best Solar Panel.
The Crucible allows you to melt Glowstone.
The Grindstone allows you to make Blades.
炼药锅可用于清洁肮脏的宝石，并可能从粉碎的圆石和地狱岩中获取金属。
Similar to Crystallizers from other mods, the NuclearCraft one can be used for turning fluids the corresponding Dusts.
中级炼金粉尘是第二个催化剂，大多数时候可以让你从炼金灌注台获得两倍的输出。
The Tier 1 Lightning Rod generates about 350kRF per strike.
You can make a Reinforced Blast Furnace and add Preheaters to it to make it run faster.
Almost every multiblock machine from IE uses at least one type of Engineering Block.
The Tier 2 Lightning Rod generates about 1.75MRF per strike.
充能使用能量，展示台上的物品每边隔3个方块远，可以为某些物品充能。
The Fuel Input Machine allows you to speed up your Smeltery, by putting Speed Upgrades and Solid Fuel in it.
With the Stirling Engine, you can generate RF from the heat of the molten fluids in Seared Tanks.
The Tier 3 Lightning Rod generates about 8.75MRF per strike.
The Fluid Agititor allows you to mix fluids and an item.
The Tier 4 Lightning Rod generates about 43.75MRF per strike.
The Tier 5 Lightning Rod generates about 218.75MRF per strike.
The Tier 6 Lightning Rod generates about 1093.75MRF per strike.
The Compression Chamber can fill up certain items with certain fluids.
The Mob Disassembler allows you to break vanilla mobs down into their basic components.
The Metal Cutting Machine allows you to make Wires, Gears Blunt Drills (that can then be turned into regular Drills with the Grindstone).
The Circuit Scribe allows you to etch patterns on Quartz Plates.
The Propane Furnace uses Propane instead of fuel to function.
The Fluid Extraction Drill simply extracts fluids from the void. In some chunks it will extract Sulphur and in some Propane.
The Chop Saw allows you to get 6 Planks from a Log and to make Quartz Plates.
The Drill Grinder allows you to make Dusts with which you can make alloys.
奇异桶可以存放大量不可堆叠的物品。
You can travel to the Aether through a portal which is a 5x4 frame of Glowstone activated with a Bucket of Water.
The Magnetizer turns Iron into a Magnet, when given a constantly repeating Redstone signal.
When exploring the Aether, you will find a few Clouds and Quicksoil.
Grout is needed for making Seared Bricks with which you'll be able to make the many multiblocks of Tinker's Construct.
你可以在菌丝上杂交胡萝卜和马铃薯来制造孢子。
The Digital Miner, when powered, can mine ores in a area. What makes it special is that you can filter what it mines.
花药台用于制作生成产能花和功能花。
白雏菊主要用于将木头转化为活木，将石头转化为活石。
魔力池用于储存魔力并在某些物品放入其中时为其注入魔力。
魔力发射器从产生魔力的花或相邻的魔力池中收集魔力，并将其传输到面向方向的方块上。
森林法杖用于配置接受魔力的方块。
火红莲从燃料中产生魔力。

这些都是注入魔力的物品。

  在 Botania 和整合包中发展所需要的主要材料是魔力钢。
原子再构机使用 RF 发射激光，该激光可以转化它击中的方块和物品。
高级炼金粉尘是第三个炼金之尘，也是游戏早期的最后一个。 它将输出乘以4和5，在每个配方之后在它们之间切换。
为了能够制作基本的匠魂工具，您将需要一些“台子”。
使用木头，您可以制作一些简单的箱子。
转移物品的最简单方法是使用木漏斗。 然而，就像普通的漏斗一样，它们不能向上转移。
In order to make certain alloys, you are going to need to build a Smeltery.
Now that you have Knightslime and Manyullyn, you can make an upgrade that will allow your Smart Output to work as a Casting Basin.
For automating the Smeltery, you are going to need a Smart Output. Be careful though, it's really fast.
The Blood Extractor is used for collecting Blood by simply having it in your inventory when killing a mob or by shift+right-clicking on Blood on the ground, where a mob took fall damage.
By throwing a Dark Gem in a 5-block-pool of Blood, it'll absorb the Blood and turn into a Dark Power Gem.

By placing Blood on the ground, it'll soon harden and you'll be able to use a Flint And Steel on it to turn it into Hardened Blood Shards, or you can you can put it in a Drying Basin or a Casting Basin to harden it and them smelt it.
The Blood Infuser simply infuses items with Blood.
The Blood Chest uses Blood for repairing items.
Now that you have Seared Bricks, you can craft a Tool Forge and with it make advanced TIC tools.
The are many upgrades that you can add to the Smart Output to suit your needs.
The Promise of Tenacity I allows your Blood Infuser to hold up to 40 buckets of Blood and unlocks a slot for Promises of Velocity or Productivity.
Promises of Velocity make your Blood Infuser work faster.
Promises of Productivity decrease the amount of Blood used in recipes in the Blood Infuser.
The Promise of Tenacity II allows your Blood Infuser to hold up to 160 buckets of Blood and unlocks a second slot for Promises of Velocity or Productivity.
The Promise of Tenacity III allows your Blood Infuser to hold up to 640 buckets of Blood and unlocks a third slot for Promises of Velocity or Productivity.
Blood trees' parts can be squeezed to obtain more Blood than the amount that was used to make them. Keep in mind that the Leaves drop Dead Bushes, so it's best to squeeze them.
You can costruct a Broom with customizable parts that allows you to fly for the cost of some Blood.
The Clossal Blood Chest is simply a larger Blood Chest.
The Sanguinary Pedestal automatically collects Blood from the ground. In order for it to collect it from mobs however, you are going to need a Spiked Plate on top of it.
The basic Calculator is used for msking basic Calculator items.
The Atomic Calculator will allow you to make the Fire Diamonds needed for Empowered Restonia Crystals.
The Scientific Calculator will allow you to make Restone Ingots, needed for making Pistons, as well as a few other Calculator items.
Alternating Flux is higher tier of energy than RF. It can be transferred, but it cannot be used in machines. For that you are going to need a Transformer.
With the Scientific Calculator, you can make a Sapling that grows Amethysts.
With the Empowerer you can make Rock Crystal Ore. You can then use the Atomic Reconstructor on a Rock Crystal to make a Floating Crystal.
The Stone Separator can separate Ores and Wood.
Link the Floating Crystal to Iron Ore to turn it into Starmetal Ore.

For making Tech Reborn Cables, you are going to need Rubber.

 To make Rubber, you are going to need to grow a Rubber Trees, collect the Sap that shows up on its Logs from time to time with a Treetap, and smelt it.
You can make portable Generators that charge up Batteries and similar items in your inventory. The most basic one is the Survivalist one.
The Basic Machine Frame is needed for making the simplest of Tech Reborn machines.

The Rolling Machine is used for making certain metal items needed for progression.

 In expert mode, this includes Buckets.
For getting Rubber from every part of a Rubber tree, extracting Fluids from Cell and a fww other things, you are going to need an Extractor.
The Compressor is used for making Plates with power.
The Alloy Smelter is a powered Iron Allow Furnace.
The Rock Cleaner uses Water and Power to automatically clean Dirty Gems and Crushed Stone and Netherrack.
The Rock Crusher uses power to automatically grind materials and has a 3 times higher chance for giving outputs.
With the Aqueous Concentrator you can automatically insert Water and with the Aqueous Deconcentrator you can automatically extract Water.
By piping Ember Shards or Crystals in an Ember Activator, you can turn them into raw Ember energy.
The Induction Smelter allows you to get some extra items from smelting.
For transferring Ember, you are going to need Ember Emitter and Receptors. They need to be connected via the Tinker's Hammer and the Emitters need a redstone signal to work.
The Mixer Centrifuge uses Ember to mix 2 different molten metals and make alloys.
Dawnstone is an alloy of Gold and Copper that can only be made in the Mixer Centrifuge.
The Stamper uses Ember and Stamps to shape molten metals.
The Magma Crucible uses power to melt certain items.
Signalum is an alloy of Copper, Silver and Redstone.
Lumium is an alloy of Glowstone, Tin and Silver.
Enderium is an alloy of Resonant Ender, Platinum and Lead.
Manyullyn is an alloy of Cobalt and Ardite.
The Electric Furnace uses parts instead of fuel to function.
The Tempering Oven allows you to make Tempred Iron Ingots and Tempered parts that last longer. In order to do that, it needs to be given a Redstone signal for a set amount of time.
The Cinder Plinth uses Ember to turn mundane materials into Ash.
The Beam Cannon usses Ember to fire a beam that can either kill a line of mobs or activate an Exchange Tablet.
Before you can get into the alchemical part of Embers, you are going to need Aspecti.

The Exchange Tablet allows you to make more advanced Embers items. The crafting process isn't simple though. In the middle you need to have the Exchange Tablet. On it, you can place items. Near it there need to be Pedestals. Every Pedestal needs to be marked with an Aspectus. Look up the recipe for whatever you want to make, in JEI, put the corresponding items on the tablet, fill up the Pedestals with the corresponding Aspecti with an amount of Ash between the amount shown and fire the Cannon at it. If the amount of Ash was incorrect, you'll get Alchemical Waste that will tell you how much you were off by.

The Stabilization Table turns charged Unprimed Energy Cores into regular Energy Cores. For that it requires Stationary Magnets 2 blocks away from it on all 4 sides, that are given a constantly repeating Redstone signal. If they aren't given a Redstone signal at the same or are given one for way too long, this machine will explode.
The Metallurgic Infuser is used for making all the different Alloys needed for crafting all the different Mekanism machines.
The Latex Fluid Extractor collects Latex from trees, slowly breaking them in the process.
The Latex Processing Unit turns Water and Latex into Tiny Dry Rubber. With that, you can make Plastic.
For obtaining Essence, you can either make a Mob Crusher that kills mobs and collects it from them or a Resourceful Furnace that can smelt 4 items at a time and produces it after they have smelted.
Osgloglas is an alloy of all the Mekanism ingots.
To make HOP Graphite, mainly needed for making Graphite Electrodes used in the Arc Furnace, you are going to need a multiblock Squeezer.
By putting Bog Earth around Water, it'll slowly turn into Peat. Peat can be used as a fuel or it can be smelted into Ash.
The Autocrafting Unit uses Gears to autocraft items. It keeps one of every items and automatically balances stacks.
传输流体的最简单方法是使用排液口和输液道。 然而，它们不能向上转移。
为了能够熔化不同的材料，您将需要陶瓷冶炼炉和一个装满熔岩的陶瓷储罐或一个在其下方装满燃料的陶瓷加热器。
为了能够铸造不同的物品，您将需要一个陶瓷浇铸台和一个陶瓷铸造盆。
大多数 AA 机器都需要铁制外壳。
When mining in the Aether, you will find Zanite and Ambrosium.
制作最简单的 AA 方块需要木质外壳。
The Biosynthesys Unit spawns to mob that drops the item in it.
You can infuse Electrum and Diamonds with Destabilized Redstone to turn them into their Fluxed version.
The Device Frame is needed for crafting TE devices.
The Chemical Oxydizer can turn certain items into fluids.
TE has its own Energy Cell that can be upgraded in several ways.
The Machine Frame is needed for crafting TE machines.
The Rotary Condensentrator can turn liquids into gases and vise versa.
The Electrolytic Separator allows you to separate fluids into gases.
N The Chemical Infuser can mix gases.
The Chemical Dissolution Chamber can turn Ores into Slurries with Sulfiric Acid.
The Chemical Washer can clean Slurries.
使用 AA 水晶，您可以制作多个可以与世界上的方块互动的方块。
The Chamical Crystallizer can turn gases into the corresponding Dusts or Crystals.
The Advanced Machine Frame is needed for making the most advanced Tech Reborn machines.
The Chemical Reactor combines 2 different types of items.
To make Tungstensteel, needed for making Dark Matter, you are going to need a multiblock Industrial Blast Furnace with at least 3000 Heat. Keep in mind that you need to fill the multiblock with Lava.
You can turn the Hot Tungstensteel into regular Tungstensteel by putting it in a Vacuum Freezer or in a Fluid Transposer with Cryotheum.
The Recyler turns items into Scrap.
Have you ever wanted to make Clay that can be shaped into any vanilla or TR item? Well now you can!
For making end-game TR materials, you are going to need a multiblock Fusion Reactor.
To turn certain Gem Dusts into Gems and Iridium Alloy Ingot into Plates, you are going to need an Implosion Compressor.

Litherite is needed for making Tier 1 ET machines.

 Left-click with the Assembler on a multiblock Controller to see all the required blocks for the multiblock, right-click to construct it and shift+right-click to pick it up.
The Tier 1 Void Ore Miner allows you to collect Erodium.
The Tier 2 Void Ore Miner allows you to collect Kyronite.
The Tier 3 Void Ore Miner allows you to collect Pladium.
The Tier 4 Void Ore Miner allows you to collect Ionite.
The Tier 5 Void Ore Miner allows you to collect Aethium.
The Tier 6 Void Ore Miner allows you to collect Prosperity Ore.
Alabaster can be obtained with a Tier 1 Void Resource Miner.
Mica can be obtained with a Tier 2 Void Resource Miner and is required to begin crafting arrays.
The Manufactory can be used as a Crusher and is the most basic NuclearCraft machine.
The Rock Crusher can crush the the various Stone types into some mildly useful materials.
The Mob Disruptor freezes mobs in place.
NuclearCraft has several alloy that can be made in the Alloy Furnace. These 3 are the most-used ones.
The Fluid Infuser infuses items with fluids. It mainly infuses radioactive isotopes with Oxygen.
The Isotope Separator can turn Ingots into the corresponding isotopes.
The Nuclear Furnace uses radioactive materials for smelting instead of fuel.

The Fission Reactor is a multiblock shaped like a box with the sides and corners being left out. It can be filled with different combinations of Cells, moderators and Coolers that will affect the time, efficiency and heat generated by the fuel you put in it.
For your Fission Reactor to work, you are going to need to keep it at a decent temperature. For that, you are going to need Coolers.
The Negative Ion Disperser is basically a Beacon that gives you every effect.
Once your Fission Reactor is properly cooled, you can add Fuel to it. In about a minute, it will become Depleted.
The Fuel Reprocessor will allow you to process the Depleted Fuel Rod.
The Tier 4 Nano Bot Beacon can hold 16 Modifiers and allows you to stack an effect up to level 4.
The Tier 3 Nano Bot Beacon can hold 12 Modifiers and allows you to stack an effect up to level 3.
Ludicrite is the most powerful material in Extreme Reactors.
Dark Matter is the main end-game resource of Sky Resources.
Quartus Alchemical Dust is the best Alchemical Dust in the game.
The Tesla Coil electrocutes nearby mobs.
Find a way to make Wither Skeletons and kill the Wither.
Dark Matter machines have the highest max heat and best speed, but use Dark Matter to function.

Antimony can be used as a replacement for Emeralds in Villager Trades.

 To make it, you need to add an Alchemical Recombulator on the side of the top block of a Mixer Centrifuge and surround it with Pedestals with Aspecti. Fill up the Pedestals with an amount of Ash between that given in JEI and if it's wrong, you'll get Alchemical Waste every few seconds, but the Ash in the Pedestals won't be used up once they have the correct amount.
The Terraneous Extractor extracts Ores from the void.
The Universal Supercharger speeds up adjacent machines.
The Conversion Wand allows you to turn one time of block in an area into another block that you've selected.
You now have everything needed for going to the End and killing the Ender Dragon, but that's not really the end of the pack, is it?
Fluix Crystals are needed for crafting many blocks or items needed for a working ME system.
Instead of making Charged Certus Quartz Crystals through Combustion, you can simply make them with a Charger.
The Tier 2 Nano Bot Beacon can hold 8 Modifiers and allows you to stack an effect up to level 2.
Before you are able to make anything from AE2, you are going to need Presses.
To make many things in AE2, you are going to need Pure Crystals, Just drop the Seeds in Water and they'll slowly grow.
To grow Crystal Seeds faster, you can make a Crystal Growth Chamber and put them in it.
For your ME system to work, you are going to need to turn RF into a different type of power.
Nano Bot Beacons are multiblocks that, when given a set amount of RF, will give you potion effects according to the modifiers they have. The Tier 1 Nano Bot Beacon can hold 4 Modifiers.
The Inscriber allows you to make Processors.
The 1K Storage Cell can store 1024 items.
The 4K Storage Cell can store 4096 items.
The 16K Storage Cell can store 16384 items.
The 64K Storage Cell can store 65536 items.
With a Matter Condenser you can also make Singularities.

The ME Controller is the heart of your ME system. Each one of its sides gives 32 channels, if channels are enabled. They can be arranged in a shapeless multiblock where one must not touch more than 3.
To view what you have stored in your ME system you are going to need a Monitor... or few.
The Conductor Mast uses Lightning to generate power and turn Fire Diamonds into Electric Diamonds.
The Flawless Calculator allows you to make some more complex vanilla and Calculator items.
With the Atomic Calulator, you can make a Sapling that grows Tanzanite.
By combining the Amethyst and Tanzanite Sapling, you can make a.... Pear Sapling....
With the Flawless Calculator, you can make a Diamond Sapling.
The Hunger Processor store hunger points and the Hunger Module slowly regenerates your hunger when it's in your inventory.
The Health Processor store health points and the Health Module slowly regenerates your health when it's in your inventory.

The Time in a Bottle allows you to speed up blocks using the time accumulated in it by having it in your inventory.
Flux is obtained by throwing Redstone into Lava.
Flux Networks allows you to make your own wireless RF network that you can insert or extract power from.
The Precision Chamber creates Dirty Circuits from Dirt and Damaged Circuits from Stone.
The Restoration and Reassembly Chamber allow you to repair Dirty and Damaged Circuits.
Electrical Steel is an alloy of Iron, Coal and Silicon.

欢迎来到现代空岛3！

  首先，您需要创建一个岛屿并完成它的第 1 阶段（获得泥土和树苗）。 你可以按“G”来了解如何做到这一点。 除了此处列出的 6 个起始岛屿外，还有 2 个自定义岛屿，任务手册中有页面。

  如果您出于某种原因在默认世界中玩游戏，只需收集泥土和树苗。
The Painting Machine can give blocks or machines other blocks' textures.
The Industrial Machine Chassis is needed for crafting most EIO machines.
这个任务将解锁Tinker's Complement，Ceramics，Tinker's Skyblock和一些 Tinker's Construct。
The Dawnstone Anvil, in combination with the Automatic Hammer, can automatically deconstruct or repair your tools with different materials.
The Analysing Chamber analyses Circuits and has a chance to give you certain items in the process.
The Ignem Reactor consists of multiple Embers machines running together. It allows you to produce more ember from your Ember Shards.

By throwing Stardust and a Rock Crystal into Liquid Starlight, a Cluster will be created. This Cluster will slowly grow, but can be sped up by placing Starmetal Ore below it. Once it's fully grown, you can break it to obtain a Celestial Crystal.
The Starlight Crafting Altar is a multiblock that has 4 more slots than the Luminous Table.
The Celestial Altar has 8 more slots than the Starlight Crafting Altar.
The Starlight Infuser multiblock allows you to transmute certain items with a chance of using up a block of Liquid Starlight.
Regular Gems are all the Gems obtained from Stone.
Dark Gems are all the Gems obtained from Netherrack.
Light Gems are all the Gems obtained from End Stone.
To start off with Silent's Gems, you are going to need Chaos Essence.
With the Material Grader you have a chance to increase a material's stats.
Passive Chaos Pylons passivly generate Chaos over time, while Burner Chaos Pylons use fuel to generate Chaos.
The Chaos Altar collects Chaos and uses it for either charging Chaos items or transmuting items.
The Chaos Orb stores Chaos and automatically charges your Chaos items.
Glow Roses are simply Roses that glow. Why not have them all?
You can craft a Chaos Node Mover to move Chaos Nodes (those glowing white orbs scattered around the world).
Solar Cells are use in making the Solar Array. The Litherite ones have an efficiecy of 48.
Erodium Solar Cells have an efficiency of 64.
Kyronite Solar Cells have an efficiency of 96.
Pladium Solar Cells have an efficiency of 128.
Ionite Solar Cells have an efficiency of 192.
Aethium Solar Cells have an efficiency of 256.
The Tier 1 Solar Array holds 9 Solar Cells.
The Tier 2 Solar Array holds 25 Solar Cells.
The Tier 3 Solar Array holds 49 Solar Cells.
The Tier 4 Solar Array holds 81 Solar Cells.
The Tier 5 Solar Array holds 121 Solar Cells.
The Tier 6 Solar Array holds 169 Solar Cells.
The Tier 1 Lunar Array generates 1152RF/t.
The Tier 2 Lunar Array generates 2304RF/t.
The Tier 3 Lunar Array generates 4608RF/t.
The Tier 4 Lunar Array generates 9216RF/t.
The Tier 5 Lunar Array generates 18432RF/t.
The Tier 6 Lunar Array generates 36864RF/t.
Magical Wood is a material from Extra Utilities that can be used for making some useful tools and can replace Boookshelves near an Enchantment Table.
The Mecanical User can automatically use items.
You can now make machines that can autocraft, that only take up 1 block and don't use anything to work.
Extra Utilities has many Generators that you can make.
The Rainbow Generator generates large amounts of power when all the other generators are running at the same time.
The regular Capacitor Bank can store 3MRF.
With an Antenna and a few other machines, you can change the biome you are in.
For this you are going to need to make a Villager farm, find one that will accept the Contract, put him in a Golden Lasso and use it to craft a Chunk Loading Ward which loads a 3x3 area of chunks
The Chicken Wing Ring allows you to glide for a while.
The Ring of the Flying Squid allows you to propel yourself upwards for a limited amount of time.
The Angel Ring allows you to fly as long as you have 32 GP.

Scrap Furnace allows you to repurpose broken components into metal nuggets to be used in making new component. §c

NOTE: §c§YY§rou will not recieve the amount of material used in the original component craft, as the process is not 100% efficient.
With an assembly line, you can now make Advanced Pressure Tubes and Compressors that can sustain more pressure.
You are now able to make a machine that turns pressure into RF and one that does the opposite.
The Enhanced Alloy Smelter can store 10 times more power and work two times faster than the regular one.
The Enhanced Combustion Generator can store 10 times more power than the regular one and is 2 times more efficient.
The Fermenter uses power, items and a fluid to create a different fluid.
The Still uses power to turn one fluid into another fluid.
油菜压榨机使用能量将油菜转化为菜籽油。 然后，菜籽油可用于原油发电机发电。
您可以使用激光中继器以无线的方式传输电力、物品和液体。
末影外壳用于制造更高级的 AA 机器和物品。
你可以升级你的烤箱来使用能量，升级你的冰箱来生产冰，还能阻止冰箱的最后一个格子禁止使用。
您可以将幻灵接口连接到方块，以便您可以远距离与它们互动。
The Material StoneWork Factory can generate Cobblestone and process it up to 4 times.
通过将油菜种子放入堆肥机中，它们会变成生物质，然后您可以将其烧成生物燃料。

The ME Security Terminal allows you to control who can access your ME system. You automatically gain access by placing it, but you can give permission to others by putting their Biometric Cards in it.
For automating with your ME system, you are first going to need Crafting Storage. Then you can add Patterns to ME Interfaces to tell them what to input and export.
With a Spacial IO you can store an area outlined with Spacial Pylons into a Spatial Cell.
For storing Cells in your ME system you are going to need either a ME Chest or Drive, with the latter being the better one.
The ME IO Port allows you to transfer data between Storage Cells.
With a Matter Condenser you can compress different items or/and fluids into a Matter Ball. You can then use Matter Balls for painting your network.
Portable Cells can be used in a network and by themselves in your inventory.
The Advanced Inscriber acts like a regular Inscriber, but it can hold stacks of items, you can lock items to its slots and it can have 2 more Upgrades. This makes it better for automation.
You can use your ME system to continously export or inport items, fluids or gases from machines.

The EMC Assembler lets you auto-craft items with the EMC stored in your EMC system. Before being able to use it, you are going to need to right-click an Alchemical Tome and put it in only one EMC Assembler in your EMC system, so your EMC system has access to your current knowledge.
The Advanced EMC Assembler can craft faster than the Basic one, as well as 2 things at a time.
The Improved EMC Assembler can craft faster than the Advanced one, as well as 4 things at a time.
农场使用能量来让它面前的农田来自动收获和种植。
充能站使物品填充能量，释能站而清空能量。
将菜籽油放入发酵桶中，它会变成精制菜籽油。
The Tier 2 EMC Cell lets you store 4M EMC in your ME system.
The Tier 3 EMC Cell lets you store 16M EMC in your ME system.
The Tier 4 EMC Cell lets you store 64M EMC in your ME system.
The Basic EMC Condenser lets you turn items that have EMC value of up to 8k EMC, which are piped into it, into pure EMC stored in your ME system.
The Advanced EMC Condenser can turn items that have up to 80k EMC, which are piped into it, into pure EMC and with a peice of Redstone Dust, you can set how Redstone signals affect it.
通过将晶化油菜种子扔进精制菜籽油中，它会变成晶化油。
通过将充能油菜种子扔进晶化油中，它会变成充能油。
手钻本质上是一把能量镐。
您可以制作一个泥土箱来存放一组泥土。
铜箱比普通箱多2行。
铁箱比铜箱多1行。
银箱比铁箱多2行。
金箱比银箱多1行。
钻石箱比金箱多3列。
水晶箱有钻石箱的空间，但你可以看到里面有什么。
黑曜石宝箱是钻石宝箱，但它具有抗爆炸性。
末影链接袋是一种便携式末影链接箱。
末影链接箱与其他具有相同颜色代码的末影链接箱共享一个库存。 您可以使用末影珍珠将它们的容量增加3个插槽，并且您可以使用钻石将它们设为私有。
末影储罐与其他具有相同颜色代码的末影储罐共享流体。 您可以使用末影珍珠将它们的容量增加80个桶，并且您可以使用 钻石将它们设为私有。
你已经完成了基本匠魂的所有任务！
废料箱是一个可以存放物品的台阶。
石质排序箱按照输入的顺序输出物品。
石质叠柜基本上是可以堆叠放在一起以增加库存空间的石箱。 它们只能从正面打开。
The Improved EMC Condenser can turn items that have up to 800k EMC into pure EMC. It can be configured to auto-input from adjacent inventories.
The Ultimate EMC Condenser can turn any item into pure EMC.
The Impulsion Wand is essentially a Grappling Hook.
The Illumination Wand allows you to place down sources of light and to illuminate blocks.
With a Telescope you can find stars in the sky and draw out the constellations on the Papers.
The Attunement Altars allows you to attune yourself or Rock/Celestial Crystals with certain constellations.
The Extreme Crafting Table has a 9x9 grid. It's needed for crafting almost everything in Avaritia.
The Neutron Collector slowly collects Piles of Neutrons.
The Thermionic Fabricator uses Molten Glass and items for making Electron Tubes and other Glass items.
You are able to make a large multiblock Farm that uses Water, RF and Fertlizer to function, but it's one of the most efficient out there.
Using a Soldering Iron, you can add Electron Tubes to Circuits, which you can then add to your Forestry machines to upgrade them.
The Grafter has a 100 percent chance of giving you Saplings from Leaves.
By having Bees near trees or with a Mutatron, you can breed trees. Keep in mind that the trees need to first be analyzed.
After a bit of Bee breeding, you'll get to hellish Bees that produce Phosphor.
您可以将作物放在作物架上，然后将2根作物架相互叠放以进行繁殖。 作物架上的植物不能用自然物质或骨粉催熟，但跳舞树仍然有效。
The Ultimate EMC assembler is the fastest and can craft 8 things at a time.
The Alveary is a much better multiblock version of the Apiary that you can add different parts to in order to acommodate the many different species of Bees.
培育作物后，您可能想知道种子是如何改良的。 为此，您可以使用种子分析仪。 日记可让您记录所有突变。
The Tier 5 EMC Cell lets you store 256M EMC in your ME system.
The Tier 6 EMC Cell lets you store 1.024B EMC in your ME system.
The Industrial Apiary is an upgradable powered Apiary.

The Mutagen Producer creates Mutagen from Redstone, Glowstone, Uranium and Yellorium and can be used in the Mutatron and Advanced Mutatron for breeding bees without any special requires, but yet with a small chance of killing the Bees.
You can collect random genes from Bees, copy them, add them to other Bees or add them to a Template.
With a full Genetic Template, Protein and Liquid DNA, you can create a Bee.
The Essence of Flase Life will allow you to create many useful items, including Dragon Eggs.
You can make a Jar in which you can display Drones.
One of the alloys IE adds is Constantan. You can easily make it in an Alloy Kiln.
Water Wheels generate a set amount of power determined by how much Water is flowing over them and Windmills generate a set amount of power determined by the weather and how high they are.
You can add Windmill Sails to your Windmills to make them generate more power.
For putting your Wire Relays on higher places, you can use Posts and Wallmounts.
The Garden Cloche uses power and Water to grow crops faster.
You can make Wires that can transfer a Redstone signal.
The Tier 7 EMC Cell lets you store 4.096B EMC in your ME system.
The Tier 8 EMC Cell is lets you store 16.384B EMC in your ME system.

The Molten Salt Fission Reactor, unlike the regular one, uses Vessels filled with molten salt fuels and Heaters filled with molten salt coolants. Both of them can be configured for inputting and outputting. Unlike in the regular Fission Reactor, in this one you can put Pipes and whatever else you need for transferring the fluids in and out of the reactor.
By combining Ethanol, made in a Fermenter and Plant Oil, made in a Squeezer, in a Refinery, you can make Biodiesel.
Core Sample Drills give you information about the resources in your chunk.
By putting a Pumpjack in a chunk that has Oil, it'll start slowly collecting it.
By putting Oil in a Distillation Tower, it'll turn into Diesel and you'll get Bitumen as a byproduct.
Lubrican is used for speeding up certain IE multiblocks.
You can make an Advanced Coke Oven and add Preheaters to it to make it run faster.
The multiblock Distillery distills Water and makes Salt in the process.
The Neutron Compressor can turn a large amount of blocks into the corresponding Singularity.
The Ultimate Stew is a combination of many fruits and vegetables. When eaten, it completely fills up your hunger and saturation.
Cosmic Meatballs are a combination of all types of meat. When eaten, they completely fill up your hunger and saturation.

菜园，当被破坏时，会给你不同的蔬菜。

市场允许您用绿宝石换取农作物和其他 HarvestCraft 物品。
养蜂场允许您从蜂王那里收集蜂蜜和蜂蜡。
您可以制作陷阱，将它们放置在合适的环境中并使用相应类型的诱饵来被动收集生物掉落物。
研磨机和压榨机可让您在不使用任何能量的情况下加工农作物和肉类。
您可以种植大豆，将它们变成豆腐，并在大多数食谱中使用豆腐代替肉类，而不是建立大型的生物养殖场。
每吃 50 种不同的食物，您就会获得一颗心，因此您会想要制作尽可能多的不同食物。 但是，要实现这一点，您将需要一些基本的厨具。

苹果酱比普通苹果具有更高的营养价值。

betterquesting:10.desc:8: No Description
In order to progress through ThaumCraft, you are going to need a few plants.
这是最大的一顿饭。
这是最大的一顿饭。
In order to start off with ThaumCraft, you are going to need the 6 basic elemental Crystals.
《傻瓜式烹饪》一书向您展示了每种食物的食谱。
使用傻瓜烹饪手册II，您可以制作一张烹饪桌。 它将允许您通过选择食物来自动制作食物，使用多方块结构中的物品。
厨柜和冰箱是多方块结构的一部分，您可以在其中储存烹饪材料。
罐子里的牛慢慢产生牛奶，水槽是无限的水源。
当食谱需要时，烤箱和吐司机会自动烹饪相应的食物。 此外，烤箱还可以存放厨具。
您可以将厨具放在厨具架上，将配料放在调料架上。
The Iridescent Altar has 4 more slots than the Celestial Altar, but during the crafting process, you are going to need to place items in Spectral Relays around it.
With the Iridescent Altar you can make Constellation Papers, if you haven't already obtained them all from Loot Bags.
With Liquid Starlight and Lava you could make a Sand generator, which drops Aquamarine Shale from time to time.
The Endest Pearl creates a shoft-lasting black hole where it's thrown.
When killing Skeletons with the Skullfire Sword, they drop Wither Skeleton Skulls.
The Seared Furnace is a large multiblock Furnace powered by Lava.
The Tinker Tank is a large multiblock Tank that can store multiple fluids at a time without them mixing.

The Thermal Evaporator is a multiblock which can contiuously turn Water into Brine, making it great for automation. It needs to have a 4x4 base and then a ring at least 2 tall. In the corners of the last layer, you place Advanced Solar Generators.

Ember's Pipes require an Extractor powered with redstone (prefferably with a Lever) for extracting, but are much faster than Factory Tech's Conveyors. They can be filtered with the Item Transfer and there is also an Item Vacuum for sucking up items and an Item Dropper for dropping them.
The Purification Chamber uses Oxygen to turn Ores into Clumps.
The Chemical Injection Chamber turns Ores and Crystals into Shards.
The Vibrank Capacitor Bank can store 5MRF.
Soularium is an alloy of Gold and Soul Sand.

The Turbine Generator is a multiblock that doesn't have a determined shape, but has a minimum and maximum amount of components.

 It uses certain fluids to generate power.
Syngas is made by mixing Water and Coal in the Syngas Producer and is used for generating power in the Steam Generator.
The Steam Turbine Generator uses Steam or Syngas to generate power.
这个任务将解锁Redstone Arsenal，Simply Jetpacks 和Thermal Expansion可以升级的东西。

You can add a Coolant Port to your Extreme Reactor to cool it with Water, but you could also add another one and right-click it with an Extreme Wrench to output Steam from your Reactor, use it in a Turbine and then pipe it back in as Water.
The Heat Exchanger uses Lava to heat up Water and generate Steam, but also slowly generates Obsidian.
The Worktable allows you to switch between conflicting recipes and can remember up to 9 recipes at a time.

Killing Chaos Dragons that get harder and harder the farther you go for obtaining Chaos Shards isn't fun. Luckly, you can now craft an Atomic Multiplier. 

 The Atomic Multiplier allows you to quadruple stackable items at the cost of 1.5GRF and 7 Circuits. Keep in mind that creative items, Legendary rewards and items from Extended Crafting and Modular Machinery are blacklisted.
The Electrolyzer allows you to separate Water into Oxygen and Hydrogen.
The Infinity Catalyst is a combination of all the Singularities and utility items from Avaritia.

Infinity Ingots are what you need for crafting every creative item. They are hard to make, but luckly, once you make one, you can turn into Nuggets that you can then quadruple with the Atomic Multiplier.
With Infinity Ingots, you can make several tools with which you could destroy a dimension.
Infinity Armor is truly the best armor in the game, making you resistant to all types of damage.
您可以对作物架中的植物上使用剪枝器来获取它们的种子，您可以将其种植在其他作物架上。 这基本上允许您复制作物。
The Insightful Condenser collects experience in a large area in front of it.
您可以用最基本的种子来杂交出胡萝卜和甘蔗。
您可以制作号角，使用时会摧毁附近的某些方块。
代替手动使用号角，您可以制作被魔力爆发击中时激活的号角。
光环之戒佩戴时会被动产生魔力。
炼金催化器，当放置在你的魔力池下方时，你可以用它转化更多的物品。
炼造催化器当放置在你的魔力池下方时，允许你用它复制某些物品。
魔力脉冲枪理论上是便携式的魔力发射器，即您可以使用它们手动发射魔力。
您可以在植物酿造台为熏香注入药水效果，然后将其放在香盘上，以将药水效果应用于 30 格范围内的所有玩家。
污血吊坠可以通过植物酿造台注入药水效果，佩戴后，只要您有足够的魔力，就会对您施加药水效果。
The Arcane Ensorcellator uses certain items and Essence of Knowledge to create enchantments.

The Heat Exchanger is a shapeless multiblock structure that uses Hot salt coolants to heat up Water into Steam or Superheated Steam, which can be used for power, making the coolants reusable in the process. That will only happen if the hot coolant and Water are travelling in Tubes next to each other in opposite directions.
Etherial (and Ineffable Glass) is Glass that players can go through, but no other mobs can.
The Energy Infuser charges items faster than anything else.
The Advanced Dislocator allows you to instantly teleport to a certain, already specified place.
With Mica you can make Speed, Piezo and Accuracy Modifiers with which you can replace the Null Modifiers of your ET multiblocks to upgrade them.
Heavy Water can be obtained by pumping out Water with an Electric Pump with a Filter Upgrade.
The Black Hole Unit and Tank can store large amounts of one type of items or fluid. You can put multiple of them in a Controller to be able to store even more items in one block.
你已经完成了森林生活的所有任务！
If you're playing on a server, you could send items to people in a Letter, even when they aren't online. If you aren't, I guess you could send yourself a Letter.

The Escritoire will allow you to enhance the breed chances of Bees, through a simple puzzle that you can make easier by adding Drones to it. Of course, this only works if you are breeding them the normal way.
With a Rainmaker, you can create or stop rain.

The ME Capability Adaptor allows you to connect your ME system with whatever is inside a Compact Machine, by having one inside of it, next to a Tunnel and one next to it, on the corresponding side of the block.
The Ember Spread Burst allows you to separately output Ember from all of its sides, while the Ember Funnel can concentrate Ember from multiple sources into one machine.
You can use a Hang Glider for, well, gliding around the void.
You can use an XP Drain for turning Experience on the ground or your own XP into a liquid, storable in Tanks.
The /dev/null/ will automatically collect an item you select. It will keep a stack of it and void the rest.
The Dark Matter Warper uses Dark Matter to trasmute mobs around it into other mobs. It also damages players when they are near it.
The Smart Combustion Controller allows you to fully automate combustion by selecting which items can be made in it. The items closer to the left will be made first and it can do 10 recipes/s.
Light Matter machines are the most efficient, but use Light Matter to work.

betterquesting:10.name:8: The Cold Never Bothered Me Anyway
betterquesting:10.desc:8: The Light Matter Freezer is the best Freezer in the game.
You can add a few blocks to your End Portal Core to get rid of those pests.
The Wildlife Attractor uses power, Water and Plant Matter to attract animals on top of it.
You can shift+right-click with a Health Gem to fill it up with Life Points.
You can put a Health Gem in a Life Injector in order to fill it up with the health from the mobs on top of it.
You can build a multiblock Life Infuser in order to automate the life infusion process.
Sprinklers sprinkle Water in a 9x9 area.
The Dark Matter Warper will turn Zombie Villagers into Illagers (Vindicators and Evokers).

You can add an Ancient Motive Core to tools that are on a Dawnstone Anvil for them to start gaining heat when used.

 After they've gained a good amount of heat, you can drop them into an Inferno Forge to add a modifier slot to them and then you'll be able to add certain modifiers to them with the Dawnstone Anvil.
Fans, when given a Redstone signal, push mobs.
虽然它可能是一片虚空，但您可以使用地狱来制作金农场，但最重要的是，可以从烈焰人那里获得烈焰棒。 你可以为烈焰人建造一个大型的地狱岩平台，或者你可以找到一个地狱堡垒并在上面建造。
This is the most basic chassis for the most basic Ender IO machines.
生存者钓竿是一种快速且没有耐久的钓竿，可以钓出垃圾、木头、泥土和树苗。
The 1K Fluid Storage Cell can store 1024mb of fluid.
The Compressed Rock Crusher is faster and more efficient than the regular one and can grind compressed blocks.
压缩仙人掌为您提供更多仙人掌针，减少更多生命，对怪物造成大量伤害，可以从中提取水，可以切割（您可以在其上使用压缩刀）以获得 18 个仙人掌果实，并且可以种植在压缩沙子上。
刀可用于将仙人掌切成仙人掌果实，将西瓜（块）切成9个西瓜（物品），将原木切成6块木板，将木板切成6根木棍。
The 256K Storage Cell can store 262144 items.
The 1024K Storage Cell can store 1048576 items.
The 4096K Storage Cell can store 4194304 items.
You can use Wires, similar to those from Immersive Engineering, instead of Cables for your network.

Instead of havng them as full blocks, you can turn ME Drives and Storage Cells into Fixtures that have a bit more than half the storage space, but can can share a block space with Cables, Terminals,...
You can make your ME Drives blast resistant, but they'll have less space.

You can throw Rudimentary Snares at hostile mobs and once they get white particles, you can kill them in order to obtain a Demonic Will.
The Hellfire Forge uses will to combine certain items into Reagents and tools.
You can make a Blood Altar and fill it up with your Life Points by using a Sacraficial Dagger.

Using the Hellfire Forge, you can make Arcane Ashes. When placed on the ground, they will allow you to make Sigils. One of those Sigils is the Divination Sigil that allow you to see information about the Blood Altar and your Blood network.

You can use your Blood Altar to create a Blood Orb. The Blood Orb is what allows you to interact with your Blood network. You can right-click it to transfer some of your helth to your Blood network or you can put it in a Blood Altar to add the LP in it to your network.
The Alchemy Table uses LP from your Blood network to create certain items.

The Incense Altar enhances your Sacrificial Dagger, when your near it, allowing you to use up almost all your health at once, but gives you a bonus over using your using the Sacrificial Dagger the regular way. The bonus increases by having certain natural blocks and Paths near it. After using the enhanced Sacrifial Dagger you get Soulfrey, so only use it if you have a good bonus.
You can use an Inspectoris Scandalum on your Blood Altar to see what you are going to need in order to upgrade it to the next tier. Tier 2 and 3 just require a few Blank Slates.
Instead of using a Sacrificial Dagger on yourself, you can attack mobs near the Blood Altar with a Dagger of Sacrifice to fill it up with their LP.

You can make rituals by having a Master Ritual Stone surrounded with Ritual Stones in a certain pattern and then inscribing them with the correct Elemental Insription Tools. You can make a Ritual Diviner that does all that for you.
With a tier 4 Blood Altar, you are able to make a Dusk Inscription Tool. With it you can make some more complex and useful rituals.

You can use a Demon Crucible to release the will from a Tartaric Gem into the chunk and then you can use a Demon Crystallizer to turn the will in the chunk into a Will Crystal. You'll have a chance of getting a higher tier one, that you can combine with a Tartaric Gem to upgrade it to that tier. Releasing the will from that Tartaric Gem will give you a higher chance of getting the Will Crystal for that tier and small chance for getting the one from the next tier and so on.
The Slice N' Splice uses an Axe and Shears for creating advanced EIO crafting components.
Vibrant Alloy is an alloy of Endergetic Alloy and Ender Pearls.
The regular Alloy Smelter can create EnderIO alloys and smelt 3 items at a time.
The Soul Binder uses items and mobs trapped in Soul Vials to create different items.

While other mods have Cables and Pipes, EnderIO's Conduits are probably the most useful ones to exist. You can put multiple of them in a block space and have multiple things going from and to different locations.
The Combustion Generator uses hot and cold fluids to generate RF.

Instead of using Rudimentary Snares to collect Demonic Wills, you can kill them with a Sentient Sword to fill up Tartaric Gems with will. Once you fill up a Tartaric Gem, you can make one that has a higher capacity.

By adding a Binding Reagent to an alchemy circle, it will allow you to turn Diamond tools into Bound ones. You can activate their special ability, but that will cause them to slowly drain LP from your network. When activated, the Bound Blade gives hostile mobs a chance of dropping a Blood Shard.

Although other mods allow you to teleport from a specific block to another or in a specific direction, EnderIO allows you to, using the Staff of Traveling, teleport to Teleport Anchors placed around your base. That way, as long as you're in range, you can teleport to specific blocks from anywhere.
The Soul Machine Chassis is needed for crafting all Soul EIO machines.
The Wireless Charger wirelessly charges items in your inventory in a small range.
The Attraction Obelisk can attract mobs towards it.
While there are other ways of preventing mob spawns, the Aversion Obelisk is probably the most configurable and has the biggest range.
The Weather Obelisk can change the weather by using certain fluids.
Killer Joe can use a weapon on mobs in an area in front of it. However, it requires Nutrient Destillation to work.
